Following are the steps we have followed for installing and configuring collectd and Graphite.

1.Installation and setup of the collectd package on the system.

2.Tweaked the collectd config file as per our need.

3.Added some custom scripts in the collectd conf for emiting container metrics.

4.Dockerisation of Graphite and deployment of the Graphite service .

5.Created the custom URL needed for our appliaction in Graphite.


